snippet.title: Final Fantasy X Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's a cool video that I made for Final Fantasy X. This is what a trailer would look for Final Fantasy X if it was a movie. The music that I used is Pompeii and Harappa by the E.S. Posthumus. Please rate and comment. Enjoy!

If you like this video, then I know you'll like my new 'Final Fantasy X SUPER Movie Trailer 2' video. Check it out! here's the link:

http://ca.youtube.com/watch?v=qxkkbsTdQmU&feature=user
